          "id": "pq-03",
          "parentID": "peer-book-001",
          "type": "questions",
          "text": "What does deny-by-default tooling mean in practice?",
          "answer": "Every tool call is blocked unless explicitly whitelisted. No tool is available by default — agents must earn access.",
